George Carleton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Carleton_(actor) 0 George M. Carleton (October 28, 1885 – September 23, 1950) was an American character actor of the 1940s. He was a stage actor who began a brief career, during which he appeared in over 100 films, including features, film shorts, and film serials.
